WEBVTT

00:00:00.800 --> 00:00:03.190
Well, good

00:00:03.200 --> 00:00:05.510
evening. Thank you for joining us to look at the

00:00:05.520 --> 00:00:07.670
Christmas lights;

00:00:07.680 --> 00:00:09.350
I thought that was kind of fun.

00:00:09.360 --> 00:00:11.350
Paisley's been asking—we drive by

00:00:11.350 --> 00:00:11.360
and

00:00:11.360 --> 00:00:12.950
she says, 'Daddy, I want to go look at

00:00:12.960 --> 00:00:13.830
the

00:00:13.830 --> 00:00:13.840
lights.'I

00:00:13.840 --> 00:00:15.270
said, 'Okay, let's go look at

00:00:15.280 --> 00:00:17.670
the lights.'So, I thought,

00:00:17.680 --> 00:00:19.830
why not bring you all with us?

00:00:19.840 --> 00:00:21.910
Hopefully, you had a little fun. I

00:00:21.920 --> 00:00:25.109
know it was kind of quick, but

00:00:25.119 --> 00:00:26.790
if you don't move quick, sometimes

00:00:26.800 --> 00:00:28.150
you've just got a little bit of time

00:00:28.160 --> 00:00:30.150
left walking around. Megan

00:00:30.150 --> 00:00:30.160
was

00:00:30.160 --> 00:00:32.389
ready to go, so I

00:00:32.399 --> 00:00:34.549
thought I'd bring

00:00:34.559 --> 00:00:37.350
y'all along. When you go

00:00:37.360 --> 00:00:39.510
to the Oklahoma City Zoo Lights, they're

00:00:39.520 --> 00:00:42.790
the best; it is phenomenal.

00:00:42.800 --> 00:00:45.190
They have a huge display at the Oklahoma

00:00:45.200 --> 00:00:47.830
City Zoo, and we'll go over there and

00:00:47.840 --> 00:00:50.150
look at the lights sometimes and

00:00:50.160 --> 00:00:52.630
drive through their park. They've

00:00:52.640 --> 00:00:54.630
closed off roads where you

00:00:54.640 --> 00:00:56.790
can see the animals; they're making

00:00:56.800 --> 00:00:58.549
noises as you're looking at

00:00:58.559 --> 00:01:00.310
the lights, and it's pretty

00:01:00.320 --> 00:01:01.830
cool.

00:01:01.840 --> 00:01:03.270
It's probably one of my top favorite

00:01:03.280 --> 00:01:05.189
things to do, but it's pretty expensive.

00:01:05.199 --> 00:01:09.670
I think it's

00:01:09.680 --> 00:01:12.230
about $60

00:01:12.240 --> 00:01:15.270
to go, and it only lasts about an hour, so

00:01:15.280 --> 00:01:17.670
you burn that money pretty quick.

00:01:17.680 --> 00:01:19.190
The hot

00:01:19.200 --> 00:01:21.350
chocolate's expensive, too, but it's something

00:01:21.360 --> 00:01:22.630
fun to do every once in a while.

00:01:22.640 --> 00:01:25.749
That's what we did tonight.

00:01:25.759 --> 00:01:27.350
I thought we'd come on and

00:01:27.360 --> 00:01:29.510
pray. Diana and I have been listening to

00:01:29.520 --> 00:01:31.990
Joyce again, and she's been talking about

00:01:32.000 --> 00:01:34.870
pride and things the Lord

00:01:34.870 --> 00:01:34.880
shapes

00:01:34.880 --> 00:01:36.390
when you're on

00:01:36.400 --> 00:01:38.789
that potter's wheel and the Lord's

00:01:38.799 --> 00:01:40.310
telling you, 'I want you to study this. I

00:01:40.320 --> 00:01:41.749
want you to keep going. I want you to

00:01:41.759 --> 00:01:44.310
come deeper with Me.'As I keep

00:01:44.320 --> 00:01:47.350
telling you all, the Lord said that in 2026,

00:01:47.350 --> 00:01:47.360
He's

00:01:47.360 --> 00:01:50.950
drawing the bride closer to His side. There

00:01:50.950 --> 00:01:50.960
are

00:01:50.960 --> 00:01:54.149
great days of

00:01:54.159 --> 00:01:57.429
shakings and awakenings coming, and things

00:01:57.439 --> 00:01:59.429
the Lord is about to do with the

00:01:59.439 --> 00:02:04.469
body of Christ in 2026. 2025 was

00:02:04.469 --> 00:02:04.479
for

00:02:04.479 --> 00:02:06.789
warning, but

00:02:06.799 --> 00:02:08.790
the manifestations of what He's told me

00:02:08.790 --> 00:02:08.800
are

00:02:08.800 --> 00:02:12.550
coming in 2026 will be a wake-up

00:02:12.550 --> 00:02:12.560
call—a

00:02:12.560 --> 00:02:14.630
wake-up call

00:02:14.640 --> 00:02:16.710
concerning the signs of the times

00:02:16.720 --> 00:02:18.790
of the coming of the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:02:18.800 --> 00:02:20.470
I say it over and over

00:02:20.480 --> 00:02:24.150
again.

00:02:24.160 --> 00:02:26.309
The Lord teaches me a

00:02:26.319 --> 00:02:28.550
lot about the love walk when people hurt

00:02:28.550 --> 00:02:28.560
or

00:02:28.560 --> 00:02:31.510
wound you, and you

00:02:31.520 --> 00:02:33.110
have to be quick to

00:02:33.110 --> 00:02:33.120
respond. I've

00:02:33.120 --> 00:02:34.070
said, 'Lord, what do you want me to do

00:02:34.080 --> 00:02:35.750
about this? How do you want me to

00:02:35.760 --> 00:02:38.790
handle this? I'm really ticked

00:02:38.790 --> 00:02:38.800
off.'And

00:02:38.800 --> 00:02:42.309
He says, 'Brandon, walk in love.

00:02:42.319 --> 00:02:44.949
Love never fails.'I

00:02:44.949 --> 00:02:44.959
say,

00:02:44.959 --> 00:02:46.790
'They're wrong, Lord.

00:02:46.800 --> 00:02:48.869
This is wrong. I'm upset

00:02:48.879 --> 00:02:52.309
about this.'But love takes no account of

00:02:52.309 --> 00:02:52.319
a

00:02:52.319 --> 00:02:55.750
suffered wrong. Remember that. If you

00:02:55.760 --> 00:02:58.470
want to walk higher with the fire, you

00:02:58.480 --> 00:03:01.350
must learn to walk in love, even when

00:03:01.360 --> 00:03:04.470
people do you wrong. The

00:03:04.480 --> 00:03:07.030
first reaction is always where

00:03:07.040 --> 00:03:09.589
they're really at. Is it a quick

00:03:09.589 --> 00:03:09.599
repentance?

00:03:09.599 --> 00:03:12.710
Is it an excuse

00:03:12.710 --> 00:03:12.720
for

00:03:12.720 --> 00:03:15.190
how it happened? Is it

00:03:15.200 --> 00:03:17.030
'I'm sorry,'or is it quick? That's why

00:03:17.040 --> 00:03:19.110
you can pinpoint people. But the

00:03:19.120 --> 00:03:20.710
Lord tells me that regardless of how

00:03:20.720 --> 00:03:23.110
people act or what they say,

00:03:23.120 --> 00:03:25.509
you are required to walk in love, for

00:03:25.519 --> 00:03:26.949
that's where the greater glory is.

00:03:26.959 --> 00:03:29.270
Remember what the angel said when he

00:03:29.280 --> 00:03:32.309
visited the other night?

00:03:35.040 --> 00:03:37.750
The angel with the opal armor.

00:03:37.760 --> 00:03:39.589
The glory of the Lord filled my home

00:03:39.599 --> 00:03:42.630
so strongly. It lasted for over a day after

00:03:44.879 --> 00:03:47.270
he visited. I've said

00:03:47.270 --> 00:03:47.280
before,

00:03:47.280 --> 00:03:48.869
'I don't talk to

00:03:48.869 --> 00:03:48.879
angels,'but

00:03:48.879 --> 00:03:52.390
the angel had a word.

00:03:52.400 --> 00:03:55.750
He spoke: 'The Lord

00:03:55.760 --> 00:03:59.429
has sent me to give you a message.

00:03:59.439 --> 00:04:01.429
You want to know the key to the

00:04:01.439 --> 00:04:04.070
greater glory? You want to know how

00:04:04.080 --> 00:04:05.030
you're going to walk in the

00:04:05.040 --> 00:04:07.509
manifestations in these last days, how

00:04:07.519 --> 00:04:09.910
you'll be a frontrunner instead of the

00:04:09.920 --> 00:04:11.350
one tagging behind?'We say, 'Well,

00:04:11.360 --> 00:04:13.110
that's pride.'No, there are

00:04:13.120 --> 00:04:15.350
going to be trailblazers and there

00:04:15.350 --> 00:04:15.360
are

00:04:15.360 --> 00:04:16.629
going to be those following

00:04:16.639 --> 00:04:18.789
behind. I want to be walking with the

00:04:18.799 --> 00:04:20.710
King.

00:04:20.720 --> 00:04:22.469
When He's coming back and we're riding

00:04:22.479 --> 00:04:24.230
with Him, I want my horse to be

00:04:24.240 --> 00:04:27.270
on the front row. I

00:04:27.280 --> 00:04:30.230
want to hear Him say, 'Brandon,

00:04:30.240 --> 00:04:33.030
well done,

00:04:33.030 --> 00:04:33.040
son.'No

00:04:33.040 --> 00:04:34.790
matter how much people hurt or

00:04:34.790 --> 00:04:34.800
offend

00:04:34.800 --> 00:04:36.390
you,

00:04:36.390 --> 00:04:36.400
or

00:04:36.400 --> 00:04:38.469
how much they wound you in life—whether they

00:04:38.479 --> 00:04:39.990
are

00:04:40.000 --> 00:04:43.510
close to you or not—words hurt. People

00:04:43.520 --> 00:04:45.830
hurt people. It's not always

00:04:45.830 --> 00:04:45.840
intentional;

00:04:45.840 --> 00:04:47.749
sometimes people do it

00:04:47.749 --> 00:04:47.759
ignorantly.

00:04:47.759 --> 00:04:50.710
But I'm telling

00:04:50.710 --> 00:04:50.720
you,

00:04:50.720 --> 00:04:53.590
your first response

00:04:53.590 --> 00:04:53.600
must

00:04:53.600 --> 00:04:56.390
always be love. Sometimes you have to

00:04:56.400 --> 00:04:57.830
take a step back. In my

00:04:57.830 --> 00:04:57.840
own

00:04:57.840 --> 00:04:59.990
situations, I've noticed I

00:04:59.990 --> 00:05:00.000
sometimes

00:05:00.000 --> 00:05:01.590
freak out and say things.

00:05:03.520 --> 00:05:05.590
When I get wounded, I have a

00:05:05.600 --> 00:05:10.390
tendency to explode, and

00:05:10.400 --> 00:05:13.029
the Lord says, 'Draw

00:05:13.029 --> 00:05:13.039
back.'It's

00:05:13.039 --> 00:05:15.830
like a horse you pull

00:05:15.840 --> 00:05:18.469
back. What's your first reaction?

00:05:18.479 --> 00:05:20.870
Mine is usually anger, and

00:05:20.880 --> 00:05:22.950
I'll say a lot with my

00:05:22.960 --> 00:05:27.189
mouth, but the Lord says, 'Draw back. Love

00:05:27.199 --> 00:05:30.230
never fails, Brandon. Your job is to

00:05:30.240 --> 00:05:33.110
always walk in

00:05:33.110 --> 00:05:33.120
love.'When

00:05:33.120 --> 00:05:35.029
that angel visited

00:05:35.039 --> 00:05:37.029
and

00:05:37.039 --> 00:05:39.990
said,

00:05:40.000 --> 00:05:42.070
'What is going to bring in the greater

00:05:42.080 --> 00:05:44.790
glory is a love foundation—your love

00:05:44.800 --> 00:05:47.430
walk. Where are you with your

00:05:47.430 --> 00:05:47.440
love?'It's

00:05:47.440 --> 00:05:49.830
the second time I've had angels

00:05:49.840 --> 00:05:51.430
talk to me like that.

00:05:51.440 --> 00:05:53.510
One was a couple

00:05:53.510 --> 00:05:53.520
of

00:05:53.520 --> 00:05:57.270
years ago

00:05:58.720 --> 00:06:00.070
on

00:06:00.080 --> 00:06:03.189
Valentine's Day.

00:06:03.199 --> 00:06:04.390
It was amazing.

00:06:06.560 --> 00:06:07.990
A lot of

00:06:08.000 --> 00:06:09.510
people say, 'I don't go with all

00:06:09.510 --> 00:06:09.520
that,'but

00:06:09.520 --> 00:06:11.990
it's still about love. Love never

00:06:12.000 --> 00:06:14.309
fails; God is love. The Lord said to

00:06:14.319 --> 00:06:17.029
me then

00:06:17.029 --> 00:06:17.039
that

00:06:17.039 --> 00:06:20.150
the thing he needs to know the

00:06:20.150 --> 00:06:20.160
most—what

00:06:20.160 --> 00:06:22.629
he'll be judged on the

00:06:22.629 --> 00:06:22.639
most—is:

00:06:22.639 --> 00:06:24.790
how did he treat his brethren? How did

00:06:24.800 --> 00:06:27.830
he walk in love? How do you walk in love

00:06:27.830 --> 00:06:27.840
toward

00:06:27.840 --> 00:06:30.629
your wife, your husband,

00:06:30.629 --> 00:06:30.639
and

00:06:30.639 --> 00:06:33.749
your kids? When people wound you,

00:06:33.759 --> 00:06:35.990
you don't have to allow them

00:06:36.000 --> 00:06:39.189
to keep hurting you, but your reaction to

00:06:39.199 --> 00:06:43.909
them is love. Now, trust is earned; I

00:06:43.919 --> 00:06:45.350
want you to understand that. It

00:06:45.350 --> 00:06:45.360
doesn't

00:06:45.360 --> 00:06:47.430
mean you trust everybody

00:06:47.430 --> 00:06:47.440
or

00:06:47.440 --> 00:06:49.029
let everyone into your circle.

00:06:49.039 --> 00:06:50.390
In fact, the first thing the Lord

00:06:50.400 --> 00:06:52.070
told me when I started

00:06:52.080 --> 00:06:54.550
this ministry was, 'Trust no one.

00:06:54.560 --> 00:06:56.230
Don't allow people in your inner circle,

00:06:56.240 --> 00:06:58.950
Brandon. There are things I will call

00:06:58.960 --> 00:07:01.029
you to do and say where you're not

00:07:01.039 --> 00:07:03.430
allowed to have friends. You'll be

00:07:03.440 --> 00:07:05.990
separated unto Me

00:07:05.990 --> 00:07:06.000
to

00:07:06.000 --> 00:07:08.390
say the hard things. There will be a

00:07:08.400 --> 00:07:11.670
target on you in the natural, and you

00:07:11.680 --> 00:07:13.990
will be required to take communion and

00:07:14.000 --> 00:07:15.909
fellowship with Me, and walk in love with

00:07:15.919 --> 00:07:18.870
your wife and

00:07:18.870 --> 00:07:18.880
kids.'I've

00:07:18.880 --> 00:07:21.830
learned even with family it's not

00:07:21.840 --> 00:07:23.909
always the easiest thing to do because

00:07:23.919 --> 00:07:25.990
they're not always going to 'get'you, and

00:07:26.000 --> 00:07:28.150
it's not required for them to get you. You

00:07:28.150 --> 00:07:28.160
are

00:07:28.160 --> 00:07:29.589
obedient unto God.

00:07:29.599 --> 00:07:31.189
The Lord even says to me

00:07:31.189 --> 00:07:31.199
regarding

00:07:31.199 --> 00:07:32.710
the

00:07:32.720 --> 00:07:35.510
emails we get, 'Fear God, not man. Fear

00:07:35.520 --> 00:07:37.350
Me, not man. Don't worry about what

00:07:37.360 --> 00:07:40.309
they're saying about you. Draw close to

00:07:40.319 --> 00:07:42.550
My side and walk with Me in this

00:07:42.550 --> 00:07:42.560
end-time

00:07:42.560 --> 00:07:44.550
harvest. Walk with Me and I'll

00:07:44.560 --> 00:07:46.870
use you greatly and

00:07:46.870 --> 00:07:46.880
mightily.'They

00:07:46.880 --> 00:07:49.670
won't understand why you're

00:07:49.680 --> 00:07:51.909
accelerating so quickly, but it's not

00:07:51.919 --> 00:07:54.230
for them.

00:07:54.240 --> 00:07:59.029
Keep humble. Keep your flesh under and

00:07:59.039 --> 00:08:03.270
keep the love walk straight.

00:08:03.280 --> 00:08:06.309
I had an

00:08:06.319 --> 00:08:09.189
opportunity this weekend to

00:08:09.199 --> 00:08:12.790
be really ticked off at some

00:08:12.800 --> 00:08:14.629
things. I'm telling you,

00:08:14.639 --> 00:08:15.990
I haven't been that

00:08:16.000 --> 00:08:18.869
mad in a long time, to the point where I

00:08:18.879 --> 00:08:21.430
was trembling. I asked, 'Lord,

00:08:21.440 --> 00:08:23.749
what do you want me to do about all

00:08:23.759 --> 00:08:25.270
this

00:08:25.270 --> 00:08:25.280
mess?'He

00:08:25.280 --> 00:08:28.790
said, "Walk in love."I said,

00:08:28.790 --> 00:08:28.800
"Are

00:08:28.800 --> 00:08:31.189
you telling me to walk in love? I'm

00:08:31.199 --> 00:08:33.589
going to go off. What do you want me to

00:08:33.599 --> 00:08:36.709
do, Lord?""Walk in love."I said, "Walk

00:08:36.719 --> 00:08:39.350
in love."The key to the greater glory,

00:08:39.360 --> 00:08:41.350
son, is even whenever you feel somebody

00:08:41.350 --> 00:08:41.360
has

00:08:41.360 --> 00:08:44.230
done you wrong—and they did—is to walk

00:08:44.240 --> 00:08:46.389
in love.

00:08:46.399 --> 00:08:48.070
Regardless of the excuses they try to

00:08:48.080 --> 00:08:49.750
make afterwards,

00:08:49.760 --> 00:08:51.509
wrong is wrong and right is right. It

00:08:51.509 --> 00:08:51.519
doesn't

00:08:51.519 --> 00:08:53.430
matter what their response

00:08:53.440 --> 00:08:55.990
is;

00:08:56.000 --> 00:08:57.430
your response is love. And that's what

00:08:57.440 --> 00:09:00.710
he said to me. And I said, "That's

00:09:00.720 --> 00:09:03.269
hard for my flesh to

00:09:03.269 --> 00:09:03.279
hear."I'm

00:09:03.279 --> 00:09:04.870
screaming inside, you know, and it's

00:09:04.880 --> 00:09:07.110
like that. Diana is upset. D is

00:09:07.120 --> 00:09:09.430
crying. And what do you do

00:09:09.440 --> 00:09:11.670
whenever you're wounded so deep by

00:09:11.680 --> 00:09:14.070
people that you love and trust? You walk

00:09:14.080 --> 00:09:16.630
in love. And that's why the Lord said,

00:09:16.640 --> 00:09:18.150
"It doesn't mean you have to keep

00:09:18.160 --> 00:09:20.389
planted there. It doesn't mean you have

00:09:20.399 --> 00:09:22.949
to keep doing these things. It's your

00:09:22.959 --> 00:09:26.310
choice. It's your choice if you want to

00:09:26.320 --> 00:09:28.870
walk in the greater glory.

00:09:28.880 --> 00:09:32.070
I will use you mightily. But God is

00:09:32.080 --> 00:09:34.870
love. It's not what he

00:09:34.880 --> 00:09:37.269
does; it's who he is."And if you want to

00:09:37.279 --> 00:09:39.990
walk by his side, even whenever it's

00:09:40.000 --> 00:09:42.150
something innocent or not innocent, it

00:09:42.160 --> 00:09:44.949
doesn't matter. I'm not looking at them;

00:09:44.959 --> 00:09:47.030
I'm looking at him. I'm staying

00:09:47.040 --> 00:09:49.910
vertical. And you must learn to stay

00:09:49.920 --> 00:09:52.870
vertical in these days ahead. The Lord

00:09:52.880 --> 00:09:54.870
showed me as I was walking even at

00:09:54.870 --> 00:09:54.880
Rhema

00:09:54.880 --> 00:09:56.710
tonight, he said, "You must

00:09:56.720 --> 00:09:59.829
learn to stay vertical.

00:09:59.839 --> 00:10:01.430
It's not always going to be easy because

00:10:01.440 --> 00:10:03.110
the devil wants you to go horizontal and

00:10:03.120 --> 00:10:04.230
look at everybody else and what they're

00:10:04.230 --> 00:10:04.240
doing."But

00:10:04.240 --> 00:10:06.150
what about them?

00:10:06.160 --> 00:10:08.310
How come them? And he

00:10:08.320 --> 00:10:10.230
said, "No, stay vertical. Who cares

00:10:10.240 --> 00:10:12.470
about what they're doing? Your job is to

00:10:12.480 --> 00:10:14.949
be the branch and stay on the

00:10:14.959 --> 00:10:17.829
vine. Your job is to keep looking at

00:10:17.829 --> 00:10:17.839
me."Because

00:10:17.839 --> 00:10:20.230
if you look at what's

00:10:20.240 --> 00:10:22.790
around you, your pride sets in and you

00:10:22.800 --> 00:10:26.389
start thinking, "Woe

00:10:26.389 --> 00:10:26.399
is me."You

00:10:26.399 --> 00:10:30.069
start singing a sad song,

00:10:30.079 --> 00:10:32.150
and everybody has a sad song they can

00:10:32.160 --> 00:10:34.949
sing about how people do you wrong or

00:10:34.959 --> 00:10:36.630
how people might have not done it

00:10:36.630 --> 00:10:36.640
intentionally

00:10:36.640 --> 00:10:38.710
or whatever. It doesn't

00:10:38.720 --> 00:10:41.269
matter. Your job is to always maintain

00:10:41.279 --> 00:10:42.870
love.

00:10:42.880 --> 00:10:44.790
Now, love doesn't mean you have to keep

00:10:44.800 --> 00:10:46.790
doing the same thing over and over again

00:10:46.800 --> 00:10:49.190
and allowing people to hurt you. The

00:10:49.200 --> 00:10:51.430
lesson is: don't allow people in your

00:10:51.440 --> 00:10:55.030
inner circle. I've

00:10:55.030 --> 00:10:55.040
learned

00:10:55.040 --> 00:10:57.110
a lot, and I'm trying to teach you

00:10:57.120 --> 00:10:59.430
all something because Brandon and I have

00:10:59.430 --> 00:10:59.440
learned

00:10:59.440 --> 00:11:01.430
a lot as we walk down the

00:11:01.440 --> 00:11:03.750
road. This has not been an easy journey

00:11:03.760 --> 00:11:06.870
for me, but I'm learning I want to walk

00:11:06.880 --> 00:11:09.269
with him.

00:11:09.279 --> 00:11:11.670
I always know when I've messed up

00:11:11.680 --> 00:11:14.310
because that anointing lifts off me. But

00:11:14.320 --> 00:11:17.509
he said, "Be angry and sin

00:11:17.509 --> 00:11:17.519
not."He

00:11:17.519 --> 00:11:18.949
said that because I don't have much of a

00:11:18.959 --> 00:11:20.949
filter sometimes when people tick me off

00:11:20.959 --> 00:11:23.430
and I just go, and that's the way he said,

00:11:23.440 --> 00:11:26.630
"Be angry and sin

00:11:26.630 --> 00:11:26.640
not."It's

00:11:26.640 --> 00:11:29.269
okay to be angry, but don't sin in

00:11:29.279 --> 00:11:32.150
your anger.

00:11:32.150 --> 00:11:32.160
Does

00:11:32.160 --> 00:11:33.269
that make sense what I'm telling

00:11:33.279 --> 00:11:35.030
y'all? So that's the lesson

00:11:35.040 --> 00:11:38.710
I've been learning in the last 48 hours:

00:11:38.720 --> 00:11:41.990
Be angry, sin not, walk in love. You

00:11:42.000 --> 00:11:45.190
must learn to walk in love; it's the

00:11:45.200 --> 00:11:48.150
only way to the greater glory.

00:11:48.160 --> 00:11:51.430
Remember the angel. He says

00:11:51.440 --> 00:11:53.750
it's always those life lessons;

00:11:53.760 --> 00:11:56.069
that's how we're going to walk with him.

00:11:56.079 --> 00:11:58.230
Even whenever

00:11:58.240 --> 00:12:00.310
people talk trash about you

00:12:00.310 --> 00:12:00.320
or

00:12:00.320 --> 00:12:02.550
run you down, your job is

00:12:02.560 --> 00:12:04.550
always to stay on the love side.

00:12:04.560 --> 00:12:06.790
Remember that because you're going to be

00:12:06.800 --> 00:12:09.668
tested just like Brandon is tested.

00:12:10.560 --> 00:12:12.710
But hopefully, you can learn from our

00:12:12.720 --> 00:12:14.310
mistakes.

00:12:14.320 --> 00:12:17.269
So be very careful who you let in your

00:12:17.279 --> 00:12:19.990
inner courts. Be careful who you let in

00:12:20.000 --> 00:12:23.030
your inner tent. Be careful who's

00:12:23.040 --> 00:12:26.310
influencing you. Watch who's speaking

00:12:26.320 --> 00:12:29.670
into your life. Watch where

00:12:29.680 --> 00:12:31.670
you're feeding.

00:12:31.680 --> 00:12:33.350
Make sure you're growing and you're

00:12:33.360 --> 00:12:35.829
going from glory to glory. It's your

00:12:35.839 --> 00:12:38.550
responsibility to monitor your

00:12:38.560 --> 00:12:42.629
thermostat. If your thermostat is cold,

00:12:42.639 --> 00:12:45.030
check your thermostat

00:12:45.040 --> 00:12:47.509
spiritually. You say, "I'm going to a

00:12:47.519 --> 00:12:49.750
church that doesn't feed me. I'm

00:12:49.760 --> 00:12:52.069
hanging around people who pull me

00:12:52.069 --> 00:12:52.079
down."Check

00:12:52.079 --> 00:12:54.389
your thermostat. There are many of

00:12:54.399 --> 00:12:56.629
you that say, "Well, I'm married

00:12:56.639 --> 00:12:58.069
into an unequally yoked marriage,

00:12:58.079 --> 00:12:59.750
Brandon. What should I do?"Well, you

00:12:59.760 --> 00:13:00.710
shouldn't have done that in the first

00:13:00.720 --> 00:13:02.550
place, but now that you're in it, you

00:13:02.560 --> 00:13:04.550
don't get a divorce.

00:13:04.560 --> 00:13:06.790
You're in covenant. So you walk it out

00:13:06.800 --> 00:13:11.509
in love and you pray for your spouse.

00:13:11.519 --> 00:13:13.829
The Bible says, "Don't be unequally

00:13:13.829 --> 00:13:13.839
yoked

00:13:13.839 --> 00:13:15.750
with

00:13:15.750 --> 00:13:15.760
unbelievers."It's

00:13:15.760 --> 00:13:19.590
your choice. Now, if you got

00:13:19.600 --> 00:13:21.750
saved during that marriage, you keep

00:13:21.760 --> 00:13:23.430
interceding. You fast, you pray, you

00:13:23.440 --> 00:13:25.430
anoint. I would take olive

00:13:25.430 --> 00:13:25.440
oil—this

00:13:25.440 --> 00:13:27.750
is what I got from Billy

00:13:27.750 --> 00:13:27.760
Burke—and

00:13:27.760 --> 00:13:29.590
I'm telling you what, solid

00:13:29.600 --> 00:13:32.790
people, Billy Burke.

00:13:32.800 --> 00:13:35.269
You anoint their pillow with oil. You

00:13:35.279 --> 00:13:36.629
anoint them at night, and they don't even

00:13:36.639 --> 00:13:39.269
have to know you're doing it. Maybe

00:13:39.279 --> 00:13:40.790
they wake up in the morning; you

00:13:40.800 --> 00:13:42.310
put a little bit on that pillow and you

00:13:42.320 --> 00:13:44.710
anoint it. And I pray over them over and

00:13:44.720 --> 00:13:46.230
over and over again. Make your prayer

00:13:46.240 --> 00:13:49.110
petition for 2026. That's what I tried

00:13:49.120 --> 00:13:51.509
to teach you all last night.

00:13:51.519 --> 00:13:53.190
We always write the vision down of

00:13:53.200 --> 00:13:55.829
everything we're believing for every

00:13:55.839 --> 00:13:58.550
single year. Whether it's a house, we

00:13:58.560 --> 00:14:00.310
write it down. It may be something so

00:14:00.320 --> 00:14:02.310
big that you know that God is the only

00:14:02.320 --> 00:14:04.870
one that can bring it to pass.

00:14:04.880 --> 00:14:06.710
And you go, "How is that even possible?

00:14:06.720 --> 00:14:10.069
This is not possible by man's standard,

00:14:10.079 --> 00:14:13.110
but it's possible through

00:14:13.110 --> 00:14:13.120
God."So

00:14:13.120 --> 00:14:16.069
you have to write your vision down.

00:14:16.079 --> 00:14:18.550
Put it down before you.

00:14:18.560 --> 00:14:20.790
Put your love scriptures, put

00:14:20.800 --> 00:14:22.790
whatever you've got. Write the vision

00:14:22.800 --> 00:14:25.430
down. Make sure you keep that in

00:14:25.440 --> 00:14:28.069
priority and put it on a mirror,

00:14:28.079 --> 00:14:30.710
on your car visor, or by your bed

00:14:30.720 --> 00:14:32.230
where you sleep

00:14:32.230 --> 00:14:32.240
on

00:14:32.240 --> 00:14:34.710
your nightstand. Make sure you have

00:14:34.720 --> 00:14:36.710
that as something that's always in front

00:14:36.720 --> 00:14:38.629
of your face. You have to keep the

00:14:38.639 --> 00:14:40.790
vision in front of you.

00:14:40.800 --> 00:14:42.150
That's why I try to tell people all

00:14:42.160 --> 00:14:44.150
the time: if you don't have big house

00:14:44.160 --> 00:14:46.150
mentality, go drive in the big

00:14:46.160 --> 00:14:48.230
neighborhoods and get that inside of you

00:14:48.240 --> 00:14:50.710
so that you can start thinking bigger.

00:14:50.720 --> 00:14:53.590
Poverty thinks poverty; rich thinks

00:14:53.600 --> 00:14:56.470
rich. Does that make sense? If you think

00:14:56.480 --> 00:14:58.470
like a winner, you don't go around

00:14:58.480 --> 00:15:00.550
a losing baseball team or a losing

00:15:00.560 --> 00:15:02.949
football team and get winning inside of

00:15:02.959 --> 00:15:05.590
you. If they're always losing, loser is

00:15:05.600 --> 00:15:07.430
going to be inside of you. You've got to

00:15:07.440 --> 00:15:09.750
get around a winner. Go watch somebody

00:15:09.760 --> 00:15:11.990
who's a champion. You've got to get that

00:15:12.000 --> 00:15:14.150
inside of you so that it changes you

00:15:14.160 --> 00:15:17.430
from the inside out. Add the Word to it, but

00:15:17.440 --> 00:15:19.910
get a vision. Get an inward vision of

00:15:19.920 --> 00:15:22.470
who you are in Christ and know that

00:15:22.480 --> 00:15:24.310
God's created you to be more than a

00:15:24.320 --> 00:15:27.430
conqueror. You are not made to be a 'just

00:15:27.440 --> 00:15:30.389
barely getting by'person. And maybe

00:15:30.399 --> 00:15:31.910
you're almost

00:15:31.920 --> 00:15:33.509
at the championship

00:15:33.519 --> 00:15:35.990
game and then you lose. Well, you learn

00:15:36.000 --> 00:15:37.829
from the losing and you get better the

00:15:37.839 --> 00:15:39.509
next year.

00:15:39.519 --> 00:15:42.150
There is a place in God that

00:15:42.160 --> 00:15:44.069
the devil does not go when you're

00:15:44.079 --> 00:15:45.189
underneath that umbrella of the

00:15:45.199 --> 00:15:48.069
anointing. You must learn to abide in

00:15:48.079 --> 00:15:49.910
love and abide in the glory of the

00:15:49.920 --> 00:15:52.150
Lord, even whenever your flesh does not

00:15:52.160 --> 00:15:54.870
want to. There are days whenever I

00:15:54.880 --> 00:15:57.269
just go, "Oh!"Like I said, I want to

00:15:57.279 --> 00:15:58.470
pull my hair out, and it's already pulled

00:15:58.480 --> 00:15:59.910
out.

00:16:01.440 --> 00:16:03.590
I'm trying to tell you all it's

00:16:03.600 --> 00:16:04.870
something Brandon's walking

00:16:04.880 --> 00:16:07.110
through, too.

00:16:07.120 --> 00:16:10.470
But I so want

00:16:12.639 --> 00:16:16.150
that when I get on the other side,

00:16:16.160 --> 00:16:19.189
I say, "Jesus, I did everything I could.

00:16:19.199 --> 00:16:21.430
I sure

00:16:21.440 --> 00:16:24.310
tried."I

00:16:24.320 --> 00:16:25.749
don't want to say, "Well, I didn't

00:16:25.759 --> 00:16:28.230
leave it all on the table.

00:16:28.240 --> 00:16:31.670
I wasn't all

00:16:31.670 --> 00:16:31.680
in."I

00:16:31.680 --> 00:16:34.230
think

00:16:34.240 --> 00:16:35.590
a lot of people might have regrets,

00:16:35.600 --> 00:16:37.269
ladies and gentlemen, but it's what

00:16:37.279 --> 00:16:39.269
you do

00:16:39.279 --> 00:16:40.870
with the time and the effort that you've

00:16:40.880 --> 00:16:42.629
been given.

00:16:42.639 --> 00:16:44.389
I came across a guy that was really

00:16:44.399 --> 00:16:47.189
ripped. He had muscles on muscles, and it

00:16:47.199 --> 00:16:48.470
challenges you because you look

00:16:48.480 --> 00:16:50.310
at him and go, "Wow, he has the same

00:16:50.320 --> 00:16:51.910
hours in a day as I have, but

00:16:51.920 --> 00:16:53.430
he's really trim and fit and he

00:16:53.440 --> 00:16:55.430
looks good, and then here I

00:16:55.430 --> 00:16:55.440
am."But

00:16:55.440 --> 00:16:57.350
where are you spiritually?

00:16:59.360 --> 00:17:00.710
I try to mirror myself

00:17:00.720 --> 00:17:02.389
off of Jesus, but at the same time, I'm

00:17:02.399 --> 00:17:04.150
going, "Where are people

00:17:04.150 --> 00:17:04.160
spiritually?"Where

00:17:04.160 --> 00:17:07.750
are people physically?

00:17:07.760 --> 00:17:09.270
I know I need to do better with my

00:17:09.280 --> 00:17:11.990
flesh,

00:17:12.000 --> 00:17:14.470
but I'm not satisfied with where I

00:17:14.480 --> 00:17:16.949
am spiritually either.

00:17:16.959 --> 00:17:19.029
I want more.

00:17:19.039 --> 00:17:22.549
I want to stand with Him.

00:17:22.559 --> 00:17:24.309
And the only way you're going to do that

00:17:24.319 --> 00:17:27.029
is to act like Jesus and be more like Him.

00:17:27.039 --> 00:17:28.870
And what did Jesus do, even whenever

00:17:28.880 --> 00:17:33.110
they were spitting on Him?

00:17:33.120 --> 00:17:36.390
Sometimes the best

00:17:36.400 --> 00:17:39.510
answer is no answer at all.

00:17:39.520 --> 00:17:41.750
Sometimes walking in

00:17:41.750 --> 00:17:41.760
love—whenever

00:17:41.760 --> 00:17:43.750
people are wanting a comment from you,

00:17:43.760 --> 00:17:46.950
wanting you to

00:17:46.950 --> 00:17:46.960
respond—sometimes

00:17:46.960 --> 00:17:49.029
to walk in love is not to give an answer

00:17:49.039 --> 00:17:51.029
at all.

00:17:51.039 --> 00:17:53.190
Just be still. Jesus didn't respond to

00:17:53.200 --> 00:17:56.070
it; He got quiet before

00:17:56.080 --> 00:17:57.669
them. They are the accusers of the

00:17:57.679 --> 00:17:59.430
brethren, the accusers of the

00:17:59.440 --> 00:18:03.029
palace. 'Hey, what do you say to

00:18:03.039 --> 00:18:05.830
this?'Silence.

00:18:05.840 --> 00:18:07.350
'They're accusing you. They want to put

00:18:07.360 --> 00:18:11.990
you to

00:18:11.990 --> 00:18:12.000
death.'Silence.

00:18:12.000 --> 00:18:14.630
So, His example is that not

00:18:14.640 --> 00:18:17.430
everything requires a reaction.

00:18:17.440 --> 00:18:21.270
I'm learning that too. Sometimes

00:18:21.280 --> 00:18:24.630
no words is a good thing.

00:18:28.240 --> 00:18:29.830
We're all a work in

00:18:29.840 --> 00:18:31.909
progress. We're all learning. But I want

00:18:31.919 --> 00:18:33.909
to teach you all as much as what I'm

00:18:33.919 --> 00:18:36.390
learning, especially today

00:18:36.400 --> 00:18:39.990
and yesterday. Walk in love. Walk in

00:18:40.000 --> 00:18:43.270
love. Love never fails. You either

00:18:43.270 --> 00:18:43.280
have

00:18:43.280 --> 00:18:45.430
it or you don't. Either you're a

00:18:45.440 --> 00:18:48.789
believing believer or you're not.

00:18:48.799 --> 00:18:52.070
That was 17

00:18:52.070 --> 00:18:52.080
minutes—that's

00:18:52.080 --> 00:18:57.110
not too bad for that part.

00:18:57.120 --> 00:18:59.190
I could have probably said more, but

00:18:59.200 --> 00:19:02.710
I try to save your time. And

00:19:02.720 --> 00:19:04.070
even

00:19:04.080 --> 00:19:08.070
reading

00:19:08.070 --> 00:19:08.080
Diana—she's

00:19:08.080 --> 00:19:10.310
a firecracker, too.

00:19:10.320 --> 00:19:12.630
But I tell you,

00:19:12.640 --> 00:19:14.630
listening... because the Lord told us,

00:19:14.640 --> 00:19:17.510
because we're talking about pride

00:19:17.520 --> 00:19:20.150
and Leviathan and the pride behind it

00:19:20.160 --> 00:19:23.430
and the spirits that try to be sneaky

00:19:23.440 --> 00:19:25.430
and you think you're humble. But you

00:19:25.440 --> 00:19:26.789
know what? This is something else.

00:19:26.799 --> 00:19:29.350
People say, 'Braden, you're humble.''Boy, you're humble,

00:19:29.350 --> 00:19:29.360
Brandon.'People

00:19:29.360 --> 00:19:31.510
say

00:19:31.520 --> 00:19:33.029
that all the time. Either you are or

00:19:33.039 --> 00:19:34.150
you're not. There's no

00:19:34.160 --> 00:19:36.950
pretending with humility. It's

00:19:36.960 --> 00:19:40.390
displayed

00:19:40.400 --> 00:19:43.590
by a reaction of love when you

00:19:43.600 --> 00:19:45.669
realize that it's not you doing

00:19:45.679 --> 00:19:48.150
something. You don't have to convince

00:19:48.160 --> 00:19:50.150
yourself.

00:19:50.160 --> 00:19:53.110
Either you are or you're not. I don't

00:19:53.120 --> 00:19:54.950
have to walk around and try to display

00:19:54.960 --> 00:19:56.549
humility.

00:19:56.559 --> 00:19:59.350
Either it is or it's not.

00:19:59.360 --> 00:20:00.789
'Well, Brandon, you're humble. Brandon,

00:20:00.799 --> 00:20:02.789
you're prideful. Brandon, this

00:20:02.789 --> 00:20:02.799
whatever.'Either

00:20:02.799 --> 00:20:06.470
you are or you're not.

00:20:06.480 --> 00:20:09.590
You cannot fake humility.

00:20:11.919 --> 00:20:14.070
Either it's you, either it's Jesus

00:20:14.080 --> 00:20:16.549
Christ in you, or it's not. But I don't

00:20:16.559 --> 00:20:18.789
have to vocalize it. That's why I don't

00:20:18.799 --> 00:20:20.549
ever say I try to be

00:20:20.559 --> 00:20:22.710
whatever, because I know.

00:20:22.720 --> 00:20:24.710
If you look

00:20:24.720 --> 00:20:27.029
at my resume, you know Brandon doesn't

00:20:27.029 --> 00:20:27.039
have

00:20:27.039 --> 00:20:29.830
what it takes in the natural.

00:20:29.840 --> 00:20:32.710
Do you understand? Brandon is

00:20:32.720 --> 00:20:35.830
solely dependent upon Jesus.

00:20:35.840 --> 00:20:37.350
I don't have much education. People say,

00:20:37.360 --> 00:20:39.190
'Brandon, don't knock

00:20:39.190 --> 00:20:39.200
yourself.'No,

00:20:39.200 --> 00:20:41.990
I'm stating a fact. That's

00:20:42.000 --> 00:20:43.510
not me trying to be humble; that's just

00:20:43.520 --> 00:20:47.029
stating a fact. I am

00:20:47.029 --> 00:20:47.039
flat-out

00:20:47.039 --> 00:20:49.270
nothing without Jesus Christ

00:20:49.280 --> 00:20:51.909
or my education. When you can barely

00:20:51.919 --> 00:20:54.149
read and write...

00:20:54.159 --> 00:20:55.990
things that I do read well, I've

00:20:56.000 --> 00:20:59.350
read probably a thousand times

00:20:59.360 --> 00:21:01.270
or I've studied it.

00:21:01.280 --> 00:21:04.470
If it's raw, like reading

00:21:04.480 --> 00:21:06.630
those articles that Braden puts up, you

00:21:06.640 --> 00:21:07.830
can take it to the bank: I'm going to be

00:21:07.840 --> 00:21:09.590
embarrassed.

00:21:09.600 --> 00:21:11.430
But I learned... even whenever I played games

00:21:11.440 --> 00:21:13.350
at Christmas time with people at youth

00:21:13.360 --> 00:21:15.350
parties, I would be the one hiding in

00:21:15.360 --> 00:21:16.870
the back because I was so embarrassed to

00:21:16.880 --> 00:21:18.070
play those games because they had to

00:21:18.080 --> 00:21:20.950
read and I couldn't read. I remember

00:21:20.960 --> 00:21:21.990
sitting in there and they would play

00:21:22.000 --> 00:21:23.590
those games at Christmas time and they

00:21:23.600 --> 00:21:24.630
said, 'Braden, do you want to

00:21:24.630 --> 00:21:24.640
play?'I

00:21:24.640 --> 00:21:26.470
said, 'Oh, no. I'm not

00:21:26.470 --> 00:21:26.480
interested,'and

00:21:26.480 --> 00:21:28.070
I'd make up an excuse.

00:21:28.080 --> 00:21:29.590
But really, the bottom line is I wanted to

00:21:29.600 --> 00:21:32.070
play with all my heart. I wanted to play

00:21:32.080 --> 00:21:34.390
with all my heart, but I was so ashamed

00:21:34.400 --> 00:21:36.310
that I was a teenager and I

00:21:36.320 --> 00:21:38.230
couldn't read that I

00:21:38.240 --> 00:21:39.590
didn't want to embarrass myself in front

00:21:39.600 --> 00:21:42.070
of all the high school kids. So, I would

00:21:42.080 --> 00:21:43.830
go and do something else and talk to the

00:21:43.840 --> 00:21:45.350
adults.

00:21:45.360 --> 00:21:47.909
A lot of times I'd go in and talk the

00:21:47.909 --> 00:21:47.919
Word to

00:21:47.919 --> 00:21:49.590
the mother of the party or the

00:21:49.600 --> 00:21:51.990
father

00:21:52.000 --> 00:21:54.390
because I was so ashamed that I

00:21:54.400 --> 00:21:55.750
couldn't do what the other kids were

00:21:55.760 --> 00:21:56.870
doing.

00:21:56.880 --> 00:21:58.390
That's what I developed;

00:21:58.400 --> 00:22:00.630
it was a defense mechanism.

00:22:00.640 --> 00:22:02.950
A lot of that came out of just a

00:22:02.960 --> 00:22:05.830
lot of pain. And even whenever I was

00:22:05.840 --> 00:22:07.750
a janitor and cleaning for all these

00:22:07.760 --> 00:22:10.549
years, it was the mechanism of

00:22:10.559 --> 00:22:12.310
rejection. There was so much

00:22:12.320 --> 00:22:13.750
rejection going through a lot of

00:22:13.760 --> 00:22:15.990
pastors. You know, it's like with

00:22:15.990 --> 00:22:16.000
us—nobody

00:22:16.000 --> 00:22:17.830
really cares truly about

00:22:17.840 --> 00:22:20.950
you. If I were still the janitor, nobody would

00:22:20.950 --> 00:22:20.960
give

00:22:20.960 --> 00:22:23.669
a crap. But because I have a

00:22:23.679 --> 00:22:25.430
million people following me now, people

00:22:25.440 --> 00:22:27.110
try to reach out to you. But really,

00:22:27.110 --> 00:22:27.120
the

00:22:27.120 --> 00:22:28.549
bottom line is, if you were still the

00:22:28.559 --> 00:22:29.909
janitor, they wouldn't even look your

00:22:29.919 --> 00:22:32.549
direction. They don't give a crap about

00:22:32.559 --> 00:22:35.270
you. Remember that. It's about Jesus

00:22:35.280 --> 00:22:37.029
inside of you. And when He exalts you

00:22:37.039 --> 00:22:39.909
and promotes you, people look your way.

00:22:39.919 --> 00:22:42.390
I was the janitor all the

00:22:42.400 --> 00:22:43.750
time. I went there and I cleaned

00:22:43.760 --> 00:22:46.470
90 toilets two or three times a week.

00:22:46.480 --> 00:22:48.149
And even then, they said, 'Go in there

00:22:48.159 --> 00:22:49.510
and clean your bathrooms. You

00:22:49.510 --> 00:22:49.520
aren't

00:22:49.520 --> 00:22:50.950
going to touch nobody and lay hands on

00:22:50.950 --> 00:22:50.960
anybody.'But

00:22:50.960 --> 00:22:53.029
the glory was on my hands

00:22:53.039 --> 00:22:54.950
even then.

00:22:54.960 --> 00:22:56.390
And I could lay hands on people and

00:22:56.390 --> 00:22:56.400
the

00:22:56.400 --> 00:22:58.070
power of God would hit them and cancer would

00:22:58.080 --> 00:23:00.470
fall off their face. I'll never forget

00:23:00.480 --> 00:23:02.390
this lady walked up to me while I was

00:23:02.400 --> 00:23:04.549
vacuuming the floor.

00:23:04.559 --> 00:23:07.110
Her boy was diagnosed with stage four

00:23:07.120 --> 00:23:08.789
cancer

00:23:08.799 --> 00:23:11.029
and she came up to me

00:23:11.029 --> 00:23:11.039
while

00:23:11.039 --> 00:23:13.190
I was cleaning the church and she said,

00:23:13.200 --> 00:23:16.149
'I've heard... we're desperate. There's

00:23:16.159 --> 00:23:17.830
nobody in this church that knows how to

00:23:17.840 --> 00:23:19.750
pray for anybody, but could you please

00:23:19.760 --> 00:23:22.149
pray for my son? He starts chemo in a

00:23:22.159 --> 00:23:24.789
couple of days. Can you lay hands on

00:23:24.799 --> 00:23:26.950
him? Do you see this knot on the side of

00:23:26.960 --> 00:23:29.029
his face?

00:23:29.039 --> 00:23:32.630
It's the size of an egg.

00:23:32.640 --> 00:23:37.029
Can you pray for

00:23:37.029 --> 00:23:37.039
it?'I

00:23:37.039 --> 00:23:39.909
said, 'Yes.'So, I shut the door

00:23:39.919 --> 00:23:42.390
because I didn't want to get in trouble.

00:23:42.400 --> 00:23:44.230
I opened the door and I said, 'Come

00:23:44.240 --> 00:23:46.470
on in here, buddy.'I said, 'In the name

00:23:46.480 --> 00:23:48.390
of Jesus Christ, I cursed that cancer

00:23:48.400 --> 00:23:51.590
and told it to

00:23:51.590 --> 00:23:51.600
go.'Three

00:23:51.600 --> 00:23:54.070
days later, she came back to the

00:23:54.080 --> 00:23:57.830
church crying. She said, 'Brandon,

00:23:57.840 --> 00:24:01.590
look, it's

00:24:01.590 --> 00:24:01.600
gone.'Not

00:24:01.600 --> 00:24:04.470
by what Brandon did, but by what

00:24:04.480 --> 00:24:06.950
Jesus did through Brandon.

00:24:06.960 --> 00:24:09.510
And when you realize

00:24:09.520 --> 00:24:12.950
'Christ in me, Christ in me,'that little

00:24:12.960 --> 00:24:14.470
boy's life—he didn't have to go to

00:24:14.480 --> 00:24:17.430
chemo. They went back to the doctor.

00:24:17.440 --> 00:24:18.870
They went back to the doctor and the

00:24:18.880 --> 00:24:21.590
doctor said, 'What happened?'She told

00:24:21.600 --> 00:24:23.990
him and he tried to make up an excuse

00:24:24.000 --> 00:24:27.110
that it wasn't cancer.

00:24:27.110 --> 00:24:27.120
I

00:24:27.120 --> 00:24:29.750
thought it was funny. I said, 'Isn't

00:24:29.760 --> 00:24:33.029
Jesus wonderful?'Do you understand?

00:24:33.039 --> 00:24:35.430
Jesus will meet you where you are and

00:24:35.440 --> 00:24:38.070
He loves you. But when you're going

00:24:38.080 --> 00:24:40.470
through the valley with all this

00:24:40.480 --> 00:24:43.269
pressure, like I'm learning, you're not

00:24:43.279 --> 00:24:46.390
important until you have a following in

00:24:46.400 --> 00:24:48.870
the world's eyes. But Jesus saw you as

00:24:48.880 --> 00:24:51.990
important when you were scrubbing poop.

00:24:52.000 --> 00:24:54.470
Do you understand? And so I don't get

00:24:54.480 --> 00:24:57.029
into all of the political stuff even

00:24:57.039 --> 00:24:59.590
when I'm invited to the White House.

00:24:59.600 --> 00:25:03.750
It's all a show pony. I

00:25:03.760 --> 00:25:05.852
refuse to be show ponies

00:25:07.279 --> 00:25:09.590
because you weren't there when I was a

00:25:09.600 --> 00:25:11.110
janitor

00:25:11.120 --> 00:25:14.149
and you didn't care then. So I

00:25:14.149 --> 00:25:14.159
realize

00:25:14.159 --> 00:25:16.310
the bigger the platform, the bigger the

00:25:16.320 --> 00:25:19.350
call what God has put inside of me. And

00:25:19.360 --> 00:25:23.990
regardless of how much God

00:25:24.000 --> 00:25:26.710
promotes Brandon Biggs, He always

00:25:26.720 --> 00:25:29.269
says, 'Stay the janitor, Brandon. Don't

00:25:29.279 --> 00:25:32.390
ever forget where I brought you

00:25:32.390 --> 00:25:32.400
from.'Never

00:25:32.400 --> 00:25:35.430
forget it, for you're about to

00:25:35.440 --> 00:25:37.110
enter into the second phase of your

00:25:37.120 --> 00:25:41.110
ministry

00:25:41.120 --> 00:25:42.789
and healing is going to fall out of your

00:25:42.799 --> 00:25:44.950
hands and cancer is going to

00:25:44.960 --> 00:25:47.510
dry up on a greater scale. The fire is

00:25:47.520 --> 00:25:49.110
going to drive out sickness like you

00:25:49.120 --> 00:25:51.350
wouldn't believe, son. But that's going

00:25:51.360 --> 00:25:52.950
to be the time whenever your ministry

00:25:52.960 --> 00:25:55.669
really takes off. Remember this and

00:25:55.679 --> 00:25:58.549
always keep small in your own eyes. I

00:25:58.559 --> 00:26:01.669
was out doing my yard work and He always

00:26:01.679 --> 00:26:04.789
tells me that: 'Remember to stay small in

00:26:04.799 --> 00:26:07.269
your own eyes.'And it was a

00:26:07.279 --> 00:26:09.510
flattering thing even this week. I was

00:26:09.520 --> 00:26:11.190
sent the videos of the Christmas party

