00:26:50.640 --> 00:26:52.149
was saying from the platform, talking to

00:26:52.159 --> 00:26:54.390
all those pastors who were

00:26:54.400 --> 00:26:56.470
invited to come to the

00:26:56.480 --> 00:26:59.029
Christmas party tonight. So, I thought

00:26:59.039 --> 00:27:00.549
it was really neat that they shared with

00:27:00.559 --> 00:27:03.029
me what was said. I was excited that

00:27:03.039 --> 00:27:05.110
