00:27:43.440 --> 00:27:47.110
91. You must understand Psalms 23.

00:27:47.120 --> 00:27:48.789
You must understand the authority of the

00:27:48.799 --> 00:27:50.630
believer. I always try to talk about

00:27:50.640 --> 00:27:53.669
Sister Billy. She's been such a friend.

00:27:53.679 --> 00:27:57.110
I want you to understand you

00:27:57.120 --> 00:27:59.029
must understand the authority of the

00:27:59.039 --> 00:28:01.430
believer, and you read these little books

00:28:01.440 --> 00:28:03.190
