02:30:29.280 --> 02:30:31.590
your heart. We will see you again.

02:30:33.040 --> 02:30:35.030
Tomorrow's

02:30:35.040 --> 02:30:36.070
Friday.

02:30:58.399 --> 02:31:01.670
I hope y'all

02:31:01.680 --> 02:31:03.190
have a good weekend.

02:31:07.680 --> 02:31:10.150
I plan on praying more;

02:31:10.160 --> 02:31:13.030
we know we have work to do. Where

02:31:13.030 --> 02:31:13.040
did

02:31:13.040 --> 02:31:14.870
this

02:31:14.880 --> 02:31:18.550
week go?

02:31:20.479 --> 02:31:22.230
When I get in the

02:31:22.240 --> 02:31:23.910
spirit and start praying,

02:31:23.920 --> 02:31:26.790
I go off to another planet.

02:31:30.880 --> 02:31:32.790
God bless you all. We love you. See you

02:31:32.800 --> 02:31:35.520
again soon.

